<br>
If you're seeing this on your first time launching the program, I'm sorry.
Use JBidwatcher for a while, enjoy it, feel free to
<a href="http://jbidwatcher.lighthouseapp.com/projects/8037-jbidwatcher/overview">report any problems</a>
